  "text": "We will see that C R and C L do not affect the eventual SFT solution (and we could have set them to zero without a loss of generality) but that C 0 and C 1 do. It is worth mentioning that, at this order, our scheme reproduces that of [CITATION_1] if we take C 1 = 0 and C 0 = −1, though comparison for operators with multiple integration regions is complicated by the discrepancy described in section 2.",
